Extra:
To make a command client-sided to toggle the hp bar.

Find
[CODE]if(s.startsWith("yellow:"))[/CODE]

Above that add this:


[B]Non renamed:[/B]
[CODE]
if(aString887.equals("::newbar"))
    HPBarToggle = true;
if(aString887.equals("::oldbar"))
    HPBarToggle = false;
[/CODE]

[B]Renamed:[/B]
[CODE]
if(inputString.equals("::newbar"))
    HPBarToggle = true;
if(inputString.equals("::oldbar"))
    HPBarToggle = false;
[/CODE]

